        1
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://richvillenyhistory.blogspot.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Every Sunday, the Welsh Society gathers for a service on Main Street, with the next one on August 25, 2024.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://richvillenyhistory.blogspot.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "After the Welsh Service on August 27, 2023, the Richville Historical Association hosted an open house with refreshments.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://richvillenyhistory.blogspot.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The old church beside the cemetery on Main Street was kindly donated to the Richville Historical Association.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
